title: Total non-resident travellers entering the country in Canada 2019
summary: This graph shows the Total non-resident travelers entering Canada during the year 2019 , each Month .
The graph was mostly stable from Jan to Apr , after which there is a general upward trend .
Although , there was a declining trend from Aug to Nov .
gold: This graph represents the total non-resident travellers entering Canada in 2019 . The graph starts out in January , where the number of Persons is 1.5e6 . It reaches a peak of 4.5e6 in July .
